# Claude Code Ignore File
# Excludes files/directories from Claude's context to reduce token usage
# Pattern syntax: same as .gitignore (globs, negation with !, etc.)

# ============================================================================
# CRITICAL EXCLUSIONS (Primary token savers)
# ============================================================================

# Dependencies (56,172 files, 624MB)
# Claude should NEVER need to read node_modules - TypeScript provides types
node_modules/

# Infrastructure Documentation (1,058 files, 117,518 lines)
# CLAUDE.md uses @docs/ on-demand imports - Claude shouldn't scan raw files
docs/infrastructure/

